    <content lang="en">
      <city>Bern</city>
      <title>The tax retained on behalf of the EU for 2006 amounts to CHF 536.7 million</title>
      <lead>The gross revenue generated from the imposition of Switzerland’s system of tax retention on interest payments in Switzerland on earnings liable to tax in the EU for the 2006 tax year amounts to CHF 536.7 million (for the second half of 2005 the amount was CHF 159.4 million).</lead>
